OL,3,CJersey first-time buyers scheme
OL,4,Creopens with up to 40% grants
OL,6,FProspective first-time buyers in can
OL,7,Fapply for government financial support
OL,8,Fagain as the First Step assisted home
OL,9,Fownership scheme reopens.
OL,11,FThis second phase will focus on
OL,12,Fgetting residents into three or four-
OL,13,Fbedroom family homes.
OL,15,FIt will also prioritise those who have
OL,16,Fbeen registered on the Assisted
OL,17,FPurchase Pathway for the longest and
OL,18,Fwho would benefit most from support.
