OL,3,CJersey first-time buyers scheme
OL,4,Creopens with up to 40% grants
OL,6,FApplicants must hold entitled status,
OL,7,Fbe registered on the pathway, have a
OL,8,F5% deposit, be able to access the
OL,9,Fmaximum mortgage lending available to
OL,10,Fthem and not be under offer from
OL,11,Fanother assisted purchase scheme.
OL,13,FThe initiative hopes to help 60 Jersey
OL,14,Fresidents get onto the property ladder
OL,15,Fwith up to 40% of government grants
OL,16,Ftowards the cost of a home.
OL,18,FThe scheme wasand helped 25 out of 125
OL,19,Fapplicants to get their first home.
