OL,3,CJersey first-time buyers scheme
OL,4,Creopens with up to 40% grants
OL,6,FDeputy Mezec explains: "Last time
OL,7,Fround we helped people with a variety
OL,8,Fof household types but it was largely
OL,9,Fone and two-bedroom flats.
OL,11,F"We want to help people into larger
OL,12,Fhomes as well, so your three-bed
OL,13,Ffamily homes and there will be more
OL,14,Ffocus on that this time around."
OL,16,FThe Government works with Andium Homes
OL,17,Fto run the #10 million scheme.
