OL,3,CJersey first-time buyers scheme
OL,4,Creopens with up to 40% grants
OL,6,FDominique Caunce from the organisation
OL,7,Fadds: "We were delighted with the
OL,8,Finterest shown in the first tranche of
OL,9,Fthe scheme, where the funding
OL,10,Favailable enabled us to make loan
OL,11,Foffers to 25 first-time buyers.
OL,13,F"We would encourage all those
OL,14,Funsuccessful in the first tranche to
OL,15,Fre-apply."
OL,17,FResidents have until Sunday 30 June to
OL,18,Fapply for this stage of the scheme
OL,19,Fwith the final round in September.
